<html>

<head>
<title>Signet Bank Student Loan Home Page: College Financing, Financial Aid, Student Loans</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#008040" vlink="#800040" alink="#804040">
<p align=center><a href="http://www.signet.com"><img src="images/xbtn_hom.jpg" alt="Signet Homepage Button" align=left border=0 hspace=5 vspace=5 width=100 height=89></a> <br>
