</CENTER><CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="6">Signet</FONT><SUP><FONT SIZE="2">&#174;</FONT></SUP><FONT SIZE="6"> <B>BIG HELP</B> for Small Business</FONT><SUP><B><TT><FONT SIZE="2">sm</FONT></TT></B></SUP></P>
</CENTER><P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
At Signet, we know that small business customers have specific needs which
a financial institution cannot meet simply by shrinking its commercial services
and offering them to small business customers. Signet offers a variety of
checking, savings, credit, and investment products especially designed for
the needs of the small business customer. We believe that a bank should
work as hard for your money as you do, and we're committed to helping you
make the most of what you make.</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_checkingmain.htm">Day In and Day Out</A> - Managing the day-to-day flow of business with checking, savings, and
cash management products.</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_loanmain.htm">Looking for Some Easy Money?</A> - Signet's flexible loans make it simple to eliminate cash flow problems
and better manage finances.</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_benefitsmain.htm">Will you be able to retire?</A> Will your employees? Do you offer a benefits plan to employees which lets
you attract and keep them? - Investment plans to help you and your employees
prepare for the future. <A HREF="sbiz_online.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/butn_new.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="66" HEIGHT="59" SGI_SETWIDTH SGI_SETHEIGHT SGI_FULLPATH="/var/www/htdocs/images/butn_new.gif"></A></P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_bighelpmain.htm">Big Help</A> - That's what we want to be for you. Here is a compilation of articles
and advice to help both the new business owner and the seasoned business
veteran.</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_etaxfile.htm">Electronic Tax Filing</A> - Federal law requires that the majority of businesses file their taxes electronically
by 1997. Is your business ready?</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_questionnaire.htm">Leave Your Mark</A> - Please let us know you were here by requesting more information about
any of our products or simply by giving us some feedback as to your interests and concerns.</P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_resources.htm">Additional Resources</A>- A grouping of other web sites whose topics specifically relate to the
needs of small businesses</P>
