<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Checking Information</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#008040" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#804040">
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><IMG SRC="images/logobchr.jpg" ALT="Signet Logo" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=38 BORDER=0></a>


<CENTER><a href="conindex.htm"><img src="images/xbtn_per.jpg" alt="Personal Finance Button"  border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ></a>
<FONT SIZE=+3><EM>Checking Information</EM></FONT>
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><img src="images/xbtn_hom.jpg" alt="Signet Homepage Button" border=0  height=89 width =100 align=middle></a><BR>
</CENTER>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>
Checking accounts are the most common transaction accounts in use today and can be considered the core of our personal finances.  Funds from checking accounts are used to cover a majority of our daily expenditures.<P>

Making a good choice can come down to understanding the benefits offered with todays accounts.  With improved technology and an increasing need for convenience, many accounts now provide a number of features unavailable in years past.  You can have 24 hour access to your funds through <A HREF ="/online/so1.htm">PC banking</A>, automated teller machines, have paychecks deposited the same day with direct deposit, and use funds from your checking account to pay merchants with debit cards.  To learn more about these features, select one of the categories below.<P>
<IMG SRC="images/arta_cbk.jpg" ALT="Checkbook" align=right>
<UL>
<LI><FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF="/online/so1.htm">PC Banking with Signet OnLine</FONT><SUP>sm</SUP><FONT SIZE="+1"> Banking Services</FONT></A><IMG SRC="images/50_new.jpg" ALT="What's New" ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE >
<LI><A HREF ="checkatm.htm">Automated Teller Machines (ATMs)</A>
<LI><A HREF ="checkdep.htm">Direct Deposit</A>
<LI><A HREF ="checkdeb.htm">Debit Cards</A>
<LI>It's Fun, It's Convienent: <A HREF ="trans.htm">Automated Voice Response Unit</A>
</UL></FONT>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=-1><I>Signet Bank, Member FDIC</I></FONT></CENTER>
<p><CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER>

<CENTER><p> <font SIZE=+1>For more information or to talk to
a sales representative about what Signet has to offer, please email us
at: <a HREF="mailto:info@signetbank.com">info@signetbank.com</a> or <a HREF="mailto:sales@signetbank.com">sales@signetbank.com</a></font></p>

<p>
<br><font SIZE=+1>Or, if you prefer, call us at <b>1-800-2-SIGNET</b> 24-hours<A HREF="mailto:comments@signetbank.com"></A>
a day, 7 days a week.</font></p></CENTER>

