<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Savings Information</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#008040" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#804040">
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><IMG SRC="images/logobchr.jpg" ALT="Signet Logo" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=38 BORDER=0></a>
<CENTER><a href="conindex.htm"><img src="images/xbtn_per.jpg" alt="Personal Finance Button"  border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ></a>
<FONT SIZE=+3><EM>Savings Information</EM></FONT>
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><img src="images/xbtn_hom.jpg" alt="Signet Homepage Button" border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE ></a><BR></CENTER>
<CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>As the numbers of available options increase, the task of selecting the savings tools that match your needs has become more challenging.  Even though there are many savings vehicles available, they fall into several broad categories:  savings accounts, time deposits (generally known as certificates of deposit or CDs), and Individual Retirement Accounts (IRAs).  To learn more about these categories, select one of the sections below.  Should you come across terms that are unfamiliar, use the glossary for assistance.<P>

<IMG SRC="images/arta_coi.jpg" ALT="Coin Image" align=left>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF ="saveacct.htm">Savings Accounts</A>
