<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER>

<P>

<B><A HREF="student.html">Parent's  Loans</A>  (Federal PLUS Loans)<BR></B>

Paying for your children's education can be a formidable challenge -- the cost

of tuition is rising, housing and books keep getting more expensive.  Look here

for more information about how to pay for your children's education with low

interest loans from <A HREF="csb.html"> <B>Signet Bank</B></A> (you can also

look at a <B><A HREF="repay.html">repayment chart</A></B> to estimate your

loan payment).  Make sure to take a look at the <B><A HREF="cp.html">college

planning</A></B> and the <B><A HREF="sighp3.html">alternative funding</A> </B>sections.

</P>

<P>

</P>

<P>



<B><A HREF="student.html#stafsub">Student's Loan </A>  (Federal Stafford

Loans)</B><BR> A College diploma is your ticket to the future, but you can't

get that ticket unless you can afford your education.  Look here to learn more

about easy, low interest loans available from Signet Bank.  There are <B><A

HREF="student.html#stafsub"> Stafford loans</A></B> which are based on need. 

There are also loans for people of <B><A HREF="student.html#stafusub">all

income levels.</A></B>  You can also look at a

<B><A HREF="repay.html">repayment chart</A></B> to estimate your loan payment.

  </P>

<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER>  

