<h1 align=center>Keep on Surfing the Net!<br>
</h1>
<h2 align=center>College Money Matter's<br>
Favorite Places on the<br>
World Wide Web.</h2>
<p><font size=4>Visit the </font><a href="http://www.signet.com/"><font size=4>Signet Bank</font></a><font size=4> Corporate Home Page.</font></p>
<p align=center><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" align=bottom width=474 height=15> </p>
<h4>Educational Links:</h4>
<p><img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>Visit <a href="http://www.ctown.com/">CollegeTown</a>, a virtual campus.<br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>If you're a student-athlete you'll want to visit <a href="http://www.sportstrac.com/">SportsTrac</a>.<br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14><a href="http://www.collegenet.com">Collegenet!</a> A great educational resource. <br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>A listing of hyperlinks to <a href="http://www.yahoo.com/education/universities">Colleges and Universities</a> on the WWW. <br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>The U.S. <a href="http://www.ed.gov/">Department of Education</a>.<br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14><a href="http://www.tgslc.org"> TGSLC </a>Texas Guaranteed Student Loan Corporation. </p>
<h4>Other Cool Places:</h4>
<p><img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14><a href="http://www.siskel-ebert.com">Siskel &amp; Ebert</a> give their opinions on current movies.<br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>Experience America's largest sporting event at <a href="http://www.superbowl.com">SuperBowl.com</a><br>
<img src="images/redball.gif" align=bottom width=14 height=14>Will you see your shadow on <a href="http://www.groundhog.org">Groundhog Day</a>?</p>
<p><img src="images/emailed.gif" align=bottom width=45 height=52><a href="mailto:mike.grandel@signetbank.com">Mike Grandel</a> and <a href="mailto:jennifer.trow@signetbank.com">Jennifer Trow</a> maintain Signet Bank's College Money Matters Web site.</p>
