 </P>
<P><BR>
 A new electronic banking product which will be available to small business
customers in 1997, on-line banking* will allow your business to: 
<UL>
<LI>Verify account balances and download account activity 
<LI>Electronically transfer funds between Signet business accounts   
<LI>Pay bills electronically 
<LI>Track which checks and deposits have cleared, as well as verify ATM transactions 
<LI>Categorize transactions to keep track of your spending patterns <IMG SRC="/images/xbtn_new.jpg" ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="100" HEIGHT="89" BORDER="0" SGI_FULLPATH="/var/www/htdocs/images/xbtn_new.jpg"> 
<LI>Prepare asset, expense, and income statements 
</UL>
<P>* using either the Quicken<SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP> or the Microsoft<SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP> Money software package </P>
<P>Requirements for installing Quicken<SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP> or Microsoft<SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP> Money: 
<UL>
<LI>IBM compatible computer (386 or higher) 
<LI>16 MB hard disk space available 
<LI>4 to 8 MB of RAM 
<LI>Hayes compatible modem (2400 Baud or higher) 
</UL>
