<TITLE>Signet Small Business Electronic Tax Filing</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY ALINK="#804040" VLINK="#800040" LINK="#008040" BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="http://www.signet.com"><IMG SRC="/images/xbtn_hom.jpg" ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH="100" HEIGHT="89" BORDER="0" SGI_SETWIDTH SGI_SETHEIGHT SGI_FULLPATH="/var/www/htdocs/images/xbtn_hom.jpg"></A> <IMG SRC="/images/artb_lpt.jpg" ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="100" HEIGHT="89" BORDER="0" SGI_SETWIDTH SGI_SETHEIGHT SGI_FULLPATH="/var/www/htdocs/images/artb_lpt.jpg"><FONT SIZE="7"> </FONT><FONT SIZE="6">Electronic Tax Filing</FONT></P>
</CENTER><P><BR>
 </P>
<P><BR>
 </P>
<P><BR>
 </P>
<P><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Internal Revenue Service (IRS) has issued a mandate which specifies
that all business taxpayers who paid at least $50,000 in employment taxes
during 1995 must begin paying taxes electronically starting on July 1, 1997.
The Electronic Federal Tax Payment System (EFTPS) will accept both debit
and credit Automated Clearing House (ACH) payments as part of this mandate.
Both of the Signet services listed below are designed to handle ACH credit
payments. The ACH credit option allows the small business to initiate the
tax deposit payment, offering more control over business cash flows. </P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_signetlink.htm">Signet Link</A><SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174</FONT></SUP> - an electronic banking program which combines services such as electronic
tax payment, balance and transaction reporting, automatic account reconciliation,
and direct deposit of payroll through the convenience of your business PC
and modem </P>
<P><A HREF="sbiz_TTAX.htm">TTAX</A><SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP> - allows ACH tax deposit payments to be initiated through a touch-tone
telephone or a personal computer</P>
<CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><BR>
 </P>
</CENTER><CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="/images/banr_bar.jpg" WIDTH="474" HEIGHT="15" SGI_SETWIDTH SGI_SETHEIGHT SGI_FULLPATH="/var/www/htdocs/images/banr_bar.jpg"></P>
</CENTER><CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="sbiz_signetlink.htm">Signet Link</A><SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174</FONT></SUP> | <A HREF="sbiz_TTAX.htm">TTAX</A><SUP><FONT SIZE="1">&#174;</FONT></SUP></P>
</CENTER><CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER"><A HREF="sbiz_home.htm">Small Business Main Page</A> | <A HREF="sbiz_checkingmain.htm">Checking, Savings, and Cash Management Products</A> | <A HREF="sbiz_loanmain.htm">Loan Products</A> | <A HREF="sbiz_benefitsmain.htm">Employer and Employee Benefits</A> | <A HREF="sbiz_bighelpmain.htm">Big Help</A> | Electronic Tax Filing | <A HREF="sbiz_resources.htm">Additional Resources</A></P>
</CENTER><CENTER><P ALIGN="CENTER">Want to get in touch with us directly? Call 1-800-5-SIGNET (1-800-574-4638)
Monday-Friday, 8:30-5 (ET)<BR>
or <A HREF="sbiz_questionnaire.htm"> drop us a line</A>.</P>
