<BODY><center><font size=+3><strong>Signet Banking Corp.</strong><br><em>Company History</em></font></center><p>
<font size=+1>Signet has a strong and rich corporate history, marked by innovation, stability and sound financial management. Included in the following pages are some articles highlighting specific points in our more than 200 years of providing financial services for individuals and businesses. <p> 
Read on to learn some interesting historical tidbits to amaze your friends and astound your family. 
