<DOCHDR>
http://jerome.signet.com:80/hr/benefit.html 206.151.85.34 19970124023117 text/html 5867
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Friday, 24-Jan-97 02:30:25 GMT
