<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Signet Bank's Internships</TITLE>
</HEAD>
 <BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#008040" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#804040">

 <h1 align=center><img src="images/banr_emp.jpg" ALT="Signet Employment"><br>Internships</h1>
<font size=+1>
<font size=+3>T</font size>he bold vision and strategies that power one of America's most dynamic financial corporations are now creating new opportunities for summer interns throughout the entire Signet organization.
<hr>
<h3 align=center>Share Signet's vision for the summer and see just how good you really are!</h3>
<hr><img align=left src="images/intern.gif" alt="Interns">
<font size=+3>T</font size>he remarkable contribution of information-based strategies to Signet's growth has created openings throughout our entire organization for summer interns capable of identifying and implementing profitable new strategies.
<p>
<font size=+3>F</font size>or the highly motivated self-starters selected as interns, this means the opportunity to put classroom skills into practice solving real problems while gaining practical experience in a fast-paced, demanding corporate environment that encourages both teamwork and individual initiative.
<hr>
<h3 align=center>Criteria are high, and so are the rewards.</h3>
<hr>
<font size=+3>I</font size>nternships will be awarded for eight to twelve weeks in our Richmond, Washington, and Baltimore offices, and criteria for selection are high.  There is no prerequisite for any particular discipline, but candidates should be academically outstanding; well-rounded; highly analytical; thoroughly familiar with PC-based analysis and modeling; and capable of interaction in an intense, highly visible environment.
<P>
<font size=+3>C</font size>ompensation is competitive with that of other major firms.  And while the selection implies no obligation on either side, a number of other previous interns have accepted full-time positions after graduation.
<br>
<center>
<form action="http://www.signet.com/cgi-bin/signetapp.pl" method="post">
