<title>Web Banking From Signet Online - It's Here!</title></head>
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/BACKGRND.GIF" >

<table border=0 cellpadding= 5 cellspacing=5>
<tr>
<td width=100 valign=top  bgcolor="#A8FFFF">


<a href="web_demo.htm"><img src="images/switch1.gif" alt="Frames Off!" width=100 height=30 border=0></a>
<p>
<a href="webbank_noframes_intro.htm">
<img src="images/webbank_intro.gif" alt="Introducing Web Banking" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webbank_noframes_features.htm"><img src="images/webbank_features.gif" alt="What you can do" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webdemo_noframes_quickbalance.htm"><img src="images/webbank_demo.gif" alt="See For Yourself! Demo." width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="web_noframes_enrollstart.htm"><img src="images/webbank_signup.gif" alt="Sign me up!" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webbank_noframes_faqstart.htm"><img src="images/webbank_faqs.gif" alt="Just the FAQ's" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="security_noframes.htm"><img src="images/webbank_security.gif" alt="Security" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>
</td>


<td  valign=top>
<img src="images/logo3.gif" alt="Signet Online Logo" width=200 height=43 hspace=10 vspace=0 border=0>
<P>
<font size=+3 color="#0000AA"><b>A New High Tech Option in Banking!</b></font>
<p>
You have heard about it from friends, read about it in the papers.  Maybe you've even seen our Web site before, but Web Banking is now a reality, and it is something that <b>BENEFITS YOU</b>.
<p>
Signet OnLine<sup>sm</sup> Banking Services has added its newest service
alternative: <i><b>Web Banking</b></i>. 
<p>
Wow, what a boring name to an exciting service, but do you know
what it means?
<p>
You can...
<ul>
<li>Access your Signet accounts like never before, via the Internet,
7 days a week, 365 days a year!
<li>View your most recent account activity and past statements!
<li>Transfer balances between accounts!
<li>Receive e-mail and/or faxes notifying you about account activity!
<li>Send and receive SECURE e-mail communications with our professional,
knowledgeable Signet OnLine<sup>sm</sup> customer service staff!
<li>Customize your banking screen layout!
</ul>

<p>

<p>
Best of all, this basic web service starts at the most attractive
price of:
<p>

<center><table border=2 cellpadding= 5 cellspacing=5>
<tr>
<td valign=center  bgcolor="FFFF00">
<center><font size=+2>Nothing!</font></center>
<p>
<center><font size=+2>That's right, it's FREE!<sup>*</sup></font></center>
</td>
</tr>
</table></center>
<p>
And, we plan to add enhancements which will extend your control
over your finances in the future.  Let us know if there's a banking service you'd like to do from the comfort of your home --  e-mail us!
<p>
What now?  If this sounds like something  you are ready to <a href="web_noframes_enrollstart.htm">sign
up for</a>, come this way.  If you want more information, like
<a href="webdemo_noframes_quickbalance.htm">a guided tour</a>, a deeper discussion about Signet's Web Banking
service <a href="webbank_noframes_features.htm">features and benefits</a>, or have a particular question,
see if we've answered it at our <a href="webbank_noframes_faqstart.htm">Frequently Asked Questions
(FAQs)</a>.
<p>
If you would like any information regarding the <a href="security_noframes.htm">security</a> of the
Web Banking service, follow this <a href="security_noframes.htm">security link</a>.
<P>
<center>
<a href="http://www.signet.com"><img src="images/butn_home2.gif" alt="Signet Homepage" width=77 height=64 border=0></a>
<a href="http://www.signet.com/online/"><img src="images/logo3.gif" alt="logo3.gif - 6.3 K" width=200 height=43 hspace=10 vspace=10 border=0></a>
<a href="mailto:online@signetbank.com"><img src="images/butn_contact.gif" alt="Contact Us" width="94" height="56" border="0"></a></center>
