<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Signet Web Banking Features and Benefits</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="images/BACKGRND.GIF" >

<table border=0 cellpadding= 5 cellspacing=5>
<tr>
<td width=100 valign=top  bgcolor="#A8FFFF">

<a href="web_demo.htm"><img src="images/switch1.gif" alt="Frames Off!" width=100 height=30 border=0></a>
<p>
<a href="webbank_noframes_intro.htm">
<img src="images/webbank_intro.gif" alt="Introducing Web Banking" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webbank_noframes_features.htm"><img src="images/webbank_features.gif" alt="What you can do" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webdemo_noframes_quickbalance.htm"><img src="images/webbank_demo.gif" alt="See For Yourself! Demo." width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="web_noframes_enrollstart.htm"><img src="images/webbank_signup.gif" alt="Sign me up!" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="webbank_noframes_faqstart.htm"><img src="images/webbank_faqs.gif" alt="Just the FAQ's" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>

<a href="security_noframes.htm"><img src="images/webbank_security.gif" alt="Security" width=100 height=75 border=0></a>
</td>


<td valign=top>

<font size=+2><b>The Features, The Benefits:</b></font>
<P>
The ins and outs of online web banking:  just click on the underlined
function to get a more detailed explanation and a sample of what
you'll actually see for each of the services: 
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_quickbalance.htm" ><B>Quick Balance</B></a> --  your current account balances at a glance.
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_acctdetail_recentact.htm" ><B>Account Details</B></a> --  account information in a
familiar statement format.
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_acctdetail_trans_search.htm" ><B>Transaction Search</B></a> --  search for transactions quickly by specific date, amount or check number. 
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_transfer_funds.htm" ><B>Transfer Funds</B></a> --  move your money between linked accounts to best suit your needs.  
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_notify_me.htm" ><B>Notify Me Service</B></a> --  get a reminder from us when
your account balances exceed levels you set.
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_bank_mail.htm" ><B>Bank Mail</B></a> --  communicate with us through secure messages.  You can even have us complete your service requests such as: 
<UL>
<LI>Stop payments on checks
<LI>Request fax/copy of a previous statement
<LI>Account inquiries
<LI>Order checks
<LI>Request applications
<LI>Change your address
</UL>
<P>
<a href="webdemo_noframes_options.htm" ><B>Options</B></a> --  select your favorite screen layout and
decide the length of your active session.
<P>
<hr>
<P>
