<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Bank Rapid Image</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Image Technology</I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<P><HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<STRONG><FONT SIZE=+2>I</FONT>t used to take hours, perhaps even days, to locate a specific check.  Now you can find that check in seconds with Signet Banks Rapid Image&#174 service.  This latest technology allows you to view high quality check images right on your PC.  No more time-consuming manual sorting, searching, and storing.  With Signet's Rapid Image&#174 system the information you need is always right at your fingertips.</STRONG>

<CENTER>
<TABLE CELLPADDING=5>
<TR VALIGN=MIDDLE>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#online">Rapid Image&#174 On-Line</A></STRONG></TD>

<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#docuport">Doc-U-Port</A></STRONG></TD>

</TR></TABLE></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Rapid Image&#174 CD-ROM</I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Rapid Image CD-ROM offers you the delivery of checks via images on a CD-ROM in place of the physical items.  This eliminates the need to have your checks sorted and returned to you.  Images are accessible using multiple sorting criteria.</STRONG>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Rapid Image&#174 CD-ROM:</B></FONT></CENTER>
<UL>
<STRONG><LI>Improves quality.  Image copies are superior to microfilm.
<LI>Reduces retrieval time and effort associated with physical checks and microfilm.
<LI>Reduces postage expense.
<LI>Provides easy reproduction of check images through windows cut-and-paste functionality.
<LI>Offers the ability to interface with other in-house systems.
<LI>Eliminates the need for fine-sorting and storage of checks.
</UL></STRONG>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="online">Rapid Image On-Line&#174</A></I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>After signing on to Signets Rapid Image&#174 system, you can selectively view images of checks within seconds.  You have the option of retrieving check MICR line information only, the associated image, or both.  Documents can be retrieved based on any of the following criteria:
account number, check number, check amount, or posting date.
</STRONG><BR>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Rapid Image On-Line&#174:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL>
<STRONG>
<LI>Next-day access to check clearings
<LI>Provides highly legible check images.
<LI>Allows inquiries using multiple indexing criteria.
<LI>Reduces retrieval time and effort.
<LI>Provides access to check MICR line information, check images, or both.
<LI>Provides easy reproduction of check images through Windows cut-and-paste functionality.
<LI>Allows customer to retain images at their location.
<LI>Offers the ability to interface with other in-house systems.
</STRONG>
</UL>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="docuport">Doc-U-Port</A></I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Whether or not you bank at Signet, images are available to any company having a 486 IBM-compatible PC with Windows.  Signet is an industry leader in its use of image technology for item processing.  Using this technology, Doc-U-Port  provides highly legible images of check-size documents each morning via on-line access. Signet can also provide document images via CD-ROM, providing approximately 40,000 images, front and back, per disk.  Using  Windows functionality, images can be cut and pasted directly into correspondence, printed, or faxed.</STRONG><BR>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Doc-U-Port:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL>
<LI><STRONG>Provides highly legible images.
<LI>Reduces retrieval time and effort. 
<LI>Provides easy reproduction of  images through Windows cut-and-paste functionality.
<LI>Offers the ability to interface with other in-house systems.</STRONG>
</UL>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<BR><CENTER><STRONG><A HREF="comm.htm"> Home</A> | <A HREF="disburs.htm">Disbursement</A> | <A HREF="account.htm"> Account Management</A> | <A HREF="ttax.htm"> TTax&#174</A> | <A HREF="payment.htm"> Electronic Payment</A> | <A HREF="lockbox.htm"> Lockbox</A> | <A HREF="form.htm"> Contact Us</A></STRONG></CENTER><BR>




<CENTER><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER><P>
<CENTER><TABLE COLSPEC="L20 L20 L20">
<TR VALIGN=BOTTOM><TD VALIGN=BOTTOM><A HREF="http://www.signet.com/signet/cinfo.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 VALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="images/xbtn_inf.jpg">
</A></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD VALIGN=BOTTOM><A HREF="http://www.signet.com">
<IMG BORDER=0 SRC="images/xbtn2.jpg"></A></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD VALIGN=MIDDLE>
<A HREF="http://www.signet.com/comm/home.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="images/xbtn_com.jpg"></A></TD></TR>
</TABLE></CENTER><CENTER><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.signet.com/signet/cinfo.htm">Corporate Information</A> | <A HREF="http://www.signet.com">Signet Home Page</A> | <A HREF="http://www.signet.com/comm/home.htm">Commercial Banking</A> </STRONG></CENTER><CENTER><P><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER><BR>
