</TABLE></CENTER><CENTER><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.signet.com/signet/cinfo.htm">Corporate Information</A> | <A HREF="http://www.signet.com">Signet Home Page</A> | <A HREF="http://www.signet.com/comm/home.htm">Commercial Banking</A> </STRONG></CENTER><CENTER><P><IMG SRC="images/banr_bar.jpg"></CENTER><BR>
