<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Bank Account Management</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">


<CENTER><TABLE>

<TR VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER><TD><IMG SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD></TD><TD><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><EM><B>Account Management &<BR> Information Reporting<BR> Services</B></EM></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<B><FONT SIZE=+2>W</FONT>hen it comes to obtaining up-to-date information about the status of your accounts as well as your ability to manage them for maximum benefit, Signet offers a wide range of options available including 24-hour access via both the telephone and personal computer.</B>

<CENTER>
<TABLE CELLPADDING=5>
<TR VALIGN=MIDDLE>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#SIR">Signet Information Reporting</A></STRONG></TD>

<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#microach">MicroACH</A></STRONG></TD>

</TR></TABLE></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<CENTER><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><EM>Signet Link</EM></B></FONT><FONT SIZE=1>SM</FONT></STRONG></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>The Signet Link<FONT SIZE=1>SM</FONT> Service makes it possible for small businesses to perform many banking functions using their personal computers and a modem from the convenience of their home or office.  With Signet Link<FONT SIZE=1>SM</FONT>, customers can access business checking and money market account information including previous day balances and transaction detail.  The Signet Link<FONT SIZE=1>SM</FONT> Service's account reconciliation module is designed to easily and quickly link the transaction detail from the bank with the customers accounting software package.  Businesses can transfer funds between their checking and money market accounts.  Subject to credit approval, businesses can perform direct deposit of payroll as well as make federal and state tax payments.  A business may expedite its collection process by using the ACH direct debit feature.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of the Signet Link<FONT SIZE=1>SM</FONT> Service:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Easy access to balance and transaction information.
<LI>Convenient method of transferring funds.
<LI>Ability to resolve questions faster.
<LI>Key banking services consolidated into one package.
<LI>Allows companies to automate accounting functions and manage cash.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><A NAME="SIR"><EM>Signet Information Reporting</EM></A></B></FONT></STRONG></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Signet Information Reporting (SIR) is a comprehensive reporting system with many service and security levels, providing access to timely and accurate information on designated accounts via personal computer (PC), touch-tone telephone, or fax.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Signet Information Reporting:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Provides account information when you need it.  SIR is available 24 hours a day, seven days a week.
<LI>Enables you to select specific information through pinpointing.
<LI>Provides all reports for seven calendar days for your convenience.
<LI>Provides PC access through a value added network.  The connection is a local call from most cities.
<LI>Allows touch-tone telephone access via a toll-free number.
<LI>Faxes Previous Day and Intra-Day Information and electronic reports automatically.
<LI>Enables you to view reports electronically, eliminating mailing delays.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><A NAME="microach"><EM>MicroACH</EM></A></B></FONT></STRONG></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>With MicroACH, you can create a wide range of Automated Clearing House (ACH) transactions including:  payroll, expense reimbursements, commissions, rents, leases, and trade payments.  You can initiate cash concentration transactions and payment collection activity such as repetitive billing or one-time fees.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of MicroACH:</B></FONT></CENTER>
<UL><STRONG><LI>Provides a convenient and economic method for processing ACH collections and disbursements.  
<LI>Allows you to quickly and easily originate a wide variety of transactions with greater flexibility and control.
<LI>Ensures the integrity of your transactions with security features and audit trails.  
</STRONG></UL>

