<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Bank Tax Services</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>TTAX</I></B></FONT>&#174</CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What it does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>You can pay Federal and State taxes by touch-tone phone or personal computer in less than 90 seconds.  The TTax system eliminates the need to make unnecessary trips to the bank to make tax deposits.  TTax deposits can be initiated 24 hours a day, seven days a week  right from your office.</STRONG><BR>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of the TTAX&#174 Service:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI><Eliminates check writing, tax coupons, and unnecessary trips to the bank.

<LI>Allows you to make tax deposits from the convenience of your office 24 hours a day, seven days a week.

<LI>Gives you an inexpensive, easy way to comply with various state and federal mandates for the electronic payment of taxes.

<LI>Provides all the information you need to complete your quarterly tax return  in one place with Signets optional Quarterly Activity Statement.

<LI>Avoids costly late penalties with the Signet Penalty Alert and Faxed Reminder Service.
</STRONG></UL>

