<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Bank Electronic Payment Options</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Electronic Payment Options</I></B></FONT>

<BR><HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<FONT SIZE=+1><B>Signet offers a variety of electronic payment methods which enable businesses to transfer funds safely and reliably between financial institutions, to business and governmental organizations, and individuals. Choose the method which best fits your needs or the needs of the recipient.</B></FONT>

<CENTER>
<TABLE CELLPADDING=5>
<TR VALIGN=MIDDLE>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#edi">Electronic Data Interchange</A></STRONG></TD>

<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#rapidwire">Rapid Wire&#174</A></STRONG></TD>
</TR></TABLE></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Automated Clearing House (ACH):</I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Founded in 1974, the Automated Clearing House (ACH) system is a nationwide electronic payment and collection network used by 17,500 financial institutions and 40,000 corporations. Corporate customers can originate both debit and credit transactions through the ACH network, providing corporate treasury departments with an efficient, cost-effective means of transferring funds for such applications as payroll, automatic payments, and electronic commerce.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of ACH:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Allows you to quickly and easily originate a wide variety of transactions with greater flexibility and control.
<LI>Gives you the opportunity to process a high volume of entries with increased efficiency, control, and security.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="edi">Electronic Data Interchange:</A></I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Electronic Data Interchange (EDI) is the computer-to-computer transmission of business documents in a standardized format between trading partners.  Financial EDI encompasses the electronic payment and delivery of remittance information.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of EDI:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Reduces errors significantly since payment and remittance information can be posted electronically, eliminating manual processing.

<LI>Enables you to gain better control over the settlement process, leading to better cash forecasting and use of funds.  ACH processing and financial EDI speed the receipt of usable funds.

<LI>Provides cost reductions in staffing, postage, and paper.

<LI>Strengthens trading partner relationships.

<LI>Provides the opportunity to streamline operations and increase efficiency in the treasury and accounting areas of your company.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="rapidwire">Rapid Wire:</A></I></B></FONT>&#174</CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Signet's Rapid Wire&#174  transfer service allows you to initiate and verify repetitive and non-repetitive wire transfers, as well as future-dated and internal transfers using your office personal computer.  Our Rapid Wire&#174 system also generates detailed reports giving you up-to-the-minute information on all of your incoming and outgoing wires.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Signet's Rapid Wire&#174 Service:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Reduces your wire transfer costs.  The wires you initiate through the Rapid Wire&#174 system cost less than traditional telephone requests.
 
<LI>Provides an easy to use method to transfer funds. 
 
<LI>Provides secure wire transfer access.  User codes and passwords protect against unauthorized use.  All non-repetitive and future-dated wires must be reviewed by a second authorized individual at your company.
 
<LI>Speeds your transfer of funds. Wires are reviewed and released quickly and are sent immediately to the Federal Reserve or to other Signet accounts.  The entire transaction process takes only minutes to complete.
</STRONG></UL>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<BR><CENTER><STRONG><A HREF="comm.htm"> Home</A> | <A HREF="disburs.htm">Disbursement</A> | <A HREF="account.htm"> Account Management</A> | <A HREF="ttax.htm"> TTax&#174</A> | <A HREF="lockbox.htm"> Lockbox</A> | <A HREF="image.htm"> Rapid Image&#174</A> | <A HREF="form.htm"> Contact Us</A></STRONG></CENTER><BR>

