<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Signet Bank Lockbox and Collections Products</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Lockbox & Collections<BR> Products</I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<B><FONT SIZE=+1>S</FONT>ignets Lockbox and Collections Products speed the collection of your customer payments, increase the productivity of your funds, reduce mail and processing float, and eliminate unnecessary borrowing. In addition, Signet offers enhanced services which vertically integrate traditional lockbox functions with data collection and fulfillment capabilities.  These services are designed to meet the specific needs of certain industry segments. Let us customize one for you.</B>

<CENTER>
<TABLE CELLPADDING=5>
<TR VALIGN=MIDDLE>
<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#wholesale">Wholesale Lockbox</A></STRONG></TD>

<TD><IMG SRC="images/reddot.gif"> <STRONG><A HREF="#safr">Signet Automated Fundraiser</A></STRONG></TD>

</TR></TABLE></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Retail Lockbox</I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Payments are processed at high speed using  either Optical Character Recognition (OCR) or Magnetic Ink Character Recognition (MICR) technology on state-of-the art, high speed processing equipment.  As each batch of remittances and checks/money orders are image-captured using Signet's technology, a unique batch and sequence trace number is assigned.  These same trace numbers follow the documents through the scanning process and are applied to both the document and the check/money order.  Use of consistent trace numbers facilitates simple information retrieval, research, and internal audit requirements.  When coupled with Signets Rapid Image product, which allows access to not only the remittance data but also to the  actual document images, tasks such as research and customer service become even more efficient.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Retail Lockbox:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Reduces clerical time and expense of processing payments.

<LI>Accelerates funds availability by reducing mail and processing float.
 
<LI>Provides transmission of remittance data in your file format for automated updating accounts	receivable.

<LI>Reports deposit notification information via Signet Information Reporting, FAX transmission, or telephone notification.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="wholesale">Wholesale Lockbox</A></I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What It Does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Signets Wholesale Lockbox service is designed for organizations which regularly recieve  high dollar payments or remittance documents which do not utilize OCR or MICR capabilities and/or require a more customized data capture  capability.  Examples would be companies which receive payment against purchase orders or multi-line invoices. </STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of Wholesale Lockbox:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>Reduces clerical time and expense of processing payments.

<LI>Accelerates funds availability by reducing mail and processing float.

<LI>Provides output options including customized reports, image photocopies of checks, and transmission of remittance data.

<LI>Reports deposit notification information via Signet Information Reporting, FAX transmission, or telephone notification.
</STRONG></UL>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I><A NAME="safr">Signet Automated Fundraiser</A></I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>What it does:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<STRONG>Signet Automated Fundraiser (SAFR) allows charitable and fundraiser organizations to focus on your fundraising events rather than the associated administrative processes.  By supplying such services as pledge invoicing, donation processing, database management, fulfillment servicing, and management reporting, Signet provides a viable administrative alternative to enhance your organizations fundraising abilities.</STRONG><P>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2 COLOR="#800000"><B>Benefits of SAFR:</B></FONT></CENTER>

<UL><STRONG><LI>All of the benefits of Signets lockbox services, plus...
<LI>Provides you with timely and accurate information to enhance the management of your fundraising events.
<LI>Reduces administrative overhead costs.
<LI>Routinely updates your database to ensure current and accurate data to assist in your planning capabilities and marketing efforts.
<LI>Facilitates the management of your financial information.
<LI>Provides a flexible alternative by providing outsourcing options which supply all, or part, of the administrative processes associated with your fundraiser.
</STRONG></UL>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

