<HEAD><TITLE>Testimonials</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 SRC="images/dozer.jpg"><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Don't Take Our Word For It,</I></B></FONT></CENTER>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+4 COLOR="#800000"><B><I>Here's What Our Builders Say. . . </I></B></FONT></CENTER>

<B><FONT SIZE=+2>"W</FONT>e have a long relationship with Signet and appreciate the ease of doing business with you.  Sticking by us during the difficult times has meant a lot and has strengthened our relationship.  Signet's rates and terms are competitive and your people are true professionals.  We appreciate the feeling that we are together in business for the long haul."</B><BR><CENTER><EM><STRONG><FONT COLOR="#800000">Thomas B. Teal, President - Teal Building Corp.</FONT></STRONG></EM></CENTER><BR><BR>

<STRONG><FONT SIZE=+2>"W</FONT>hen I first negotiated with Signet Bank for construction loans, I met with senior officials and expressed my feelings that many construction lenders were 'fair weather friends.'  I wanted to know Signet's attitude toward this situation.  They were quick to assure me through good times and bad they would stand by my company to establish a long term 'partnership'.  Their commitment was put to the test during the early 90's when our company went through a major stockholder buy-out and  a slow market at the same time.  They proved to be very supportive and never backed away from any commitment.  I knew for certain that I had found a lender who I could count on for years to come.  We are fortunate to have multiple lines of credit with several lenders.  However, because of the superior service and trusting relationship, the bulk of our loans are placed with Signet.  Our company has always had a wonderful relationship with the Signet personnel as they are eager to simplify our administrative 'headaches' by quickly and efficiently processing all of our requests." <BR><BR>

<CENTER>"The Construction Loan Department at Signet Bank is a superior organization."</CENTER>

<CENTER><P><EM><FONT COLOR="#800000">J. Russell Parker, III - President, Parker Lancaster Corporation</FONT></EM></STRONG></CENTER><BR>

<CENTER><STRONG><FONT SIZE=+2>"P</FONT>ricing has been very competitive.  Signet is willing to make the deal work."<BR>

<EM><FONT COLOR="#800000">Christopher Clemente, CEO, Comstock Homes</EM></STRONG></FONT></CENTER>





