<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><B>Signet will bend over backwards to provide your company with the financing flexibility you need to be successful.</B></FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1><B><UL>
<LI>Draw schedules can be designed to fit the way you build and pay your subs and suppliers.<BR><BR>
<LI>In most cases, loan fees can be deferred until you start construction or settle with your buyer.<BR><BR>
<LI>Construction financing is specifically tailored to meet the needs of your company.  It's custom financing without the custom price tag.  Funding for models, specs, and inventory lots is an integral part of the formula.
</UL></B></FONT>

