<HEAD><TITLE>Builder of the Month</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800000" ALINK="#FF0000">

<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 SRC="images/tom.jpg"><BR><CENTER><IMG SRC="images/logochr2.jpg"><BR><BR><FONT SIZE=+3 COLOR="#800000"><B>Residential Construction Finance's December Builder of the Month</B></FONT></CENTER>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>

<BR><BR><P><B>Congratulations to Tom Teal, Signet Residential Construction Finances Builder of the Month.  Tom Teal has been building homes in the Richmond area for over 25 years.  Teal is the largest home builder in Richmond and is consistently ranked among the 400 largest home builders in the United States. Teal attained its size and reputation by focusing on customer service.  The company offers over 50 standard home plans for customers to choose from.  Each plan can be customized to suit the individual needs and tastes of the buyer through the use of the Teal Homes architectural staff and computer-assisted design. 

	<P>Teal homes are in over 18 communities in the Richmond area, including AshCreek and Kings Charter in Hanover County, Foxcroft and Rivers Bend in Chesterfield, and Birkdale.  More recently, Teal Homes completed construction of 85 retirement homes in the Methodist Retirement Community of Cedarfield in Richmonds West End.  Teal was selected to build this project because of its reputation for design expertise and quality construction.  

	<P>Signet Residential Construction Finance congratulates Tom Teal and wishes him much success with all of his future home building projects.    </B><BR>

<HR WIDTH=97% ALIGN=center SIZE=5>  

<CENTER><TABLE COLSPEC="L20 L20 L20" CELLPADDING=10>
