<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Signet Loan Calculator </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#008040" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#804040">
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><IMG SRC="images/logobchr.jpg" ALT="Signet Logo" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=38 BORDER=0></a>
<CENTER><a href="conindex.htm"><img src="images/xbtn_per.jpg" alt="Personal Finance Button"  border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ></a><FONT SIZE=+3><EM>Loan Calculator</EM></FONT>
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><img src="images/xbtn_hom.jpg" alt="Signet Homepage Button" border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE ></a><BR></CENTER>

<CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=+1>If you're looking to put in a swimming pool, build a house, or send your kids to college, a loan may be right for you.  In your decision-making process you are most likely wondering, "How much is that going to set me back?"  This simple calculator will tell you your periodic payment based on the values you fill in below*.  So, if you're in serious need of a loan or just curious about what it would set you back to put in that new pool, give this calculator a try.  If you are unsure of any of the terms below, click on the <A HREF="glossary.htm">glossary</A> link at any time for some simple definitions to all that loan and credit jargon you never really understood.</FONT>
<P>
<CENTER><EM>*When actually applying for a loan, actual terms, costs, and expenses may vary. Refer to the applicable loan documents for specific information.</EM></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER>

