I expect my Annual Percentage Rate to be: <INPUT NAME="interest" TYPE="TEXT" ROWS=1 SIZE="10"><P>
I would like my total number of monthly payments to be:<INPUT NAME="numpay" TYPE="TEXT" ROWS=1 SIZE="10"><P>

<P> <CENTER><INPUT NAME="sub" TYPE="SUBMIT" VALUE="Calculate Now!" SIZE="3"><INPUT NAME="reset" TYPE="RESET" SIZE="3"></CENTER>
