<html>
<head>
   <title>Signet Installment Loans</title>
   <meta name="GENERATOR" content="Mozilla/2.0GoldB1 (Win32)">
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#008040" VLINK="#800040" ALINK="#804040">
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><IMG SRC="images/logobchr.jpg" ALT="Signet Logo" WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=38 BORDER=0></a>
<CENTER><a href="conindex.htm"><img src="images/xbtn_per.jpg" alt="Personal Finance Button"  border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE  ></a><FONT SIZE=+3><EM>Installment Loans</EM></FONT>
<a href="http://www.signet.com/"><img src="images/xbtn_hom.jpg" alt="Signet Homepage Button" border=0  height=89 width =100 ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE ></a><BR></CENTER>

<CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER><P>
<FONT SIZE=+1><p>Installment loans are a great way to fund that project or make that
purchase you've been looking forward to for so long but were never quite
sure where the money would come from. Whether it is building an addition
to your house, putting in a swimming pool, or buying a boat or new car,
an installment loan can be the best way to make it all happen.</p>

<p> With an installment loan, you can borrow the amount you need and make
monthly payments on that amount over a period of time until it is paid
off. Typically you are required to pay it off by a certain date but have
the option to pay it off at any time prior to your scheduled repayment
date, thus decreasing the total amount of interest you must pay on the
loan. (Prepayment penalties may apply to certain types of loans.  Read all loan terms carefully before borrowing.)</p>

<p>So, if you've been putting off that home improvement project, an installment
loan may be the place to start.</p></FONT>

<CENTER><FONT SIZE=-1><EM><IMG SRC="images/eqlhous.jpg">Equal Housing Lender</EM></FONT></CENTER>
<P><CENTER><img src="images/banr_bar.jpg" ></CENTER><P>
<CENTER><p> <font SIZE=+1>For more information or to talk to
a sales representative about what Signet has to offer, please email us
at: <a HREF="mailto:info@signetbank.com">info@signetbank.com</a> or <a HREF="mailto:sales@signetbank.com">sales@signetbank.com</a></font></p>

<p>
<br><font SIZE=+1>Or, if you prefer, call us at <b>1-800-2-SIGNET</b> 24-hours<A HREF="mailto:comments@signetbank.com"></A>
a day, 7 days a week.</font></p></CENTER>

