<BR><INPUT TYPE="RADIO" NAME="income" VALUE="5">More than $100,000
<BR><INPUT TYPE="RADIO" NAME="income" VALUE="4">$75,000 to $99,999
<BR><INPUT TYPE="RADIO" NAME="income" VALUE="3">$50,000 to $74,999
