<H3 ALIGN="center">Detailed Table of Contents</H3>
<P>Care and diligence have been taken in organizing and presenting the data
contained in <I>Don't Miss  Out</I>, however, Octameron does not guarantee its
accuracy. This edition contains information  relevant to the 1997/98 academic
year. The 1998/99 edition will be available in September 1997.</P>
